{"id":318910,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-河北高玉香就身患癌症被劳教、拘留提出/","date":"2013-10-20T07:17:46Z","modified":"2013-10-20T07:17:46Z","title":"维权网 | 河北高玉香就身患癌症被劳教、拘留提出控告（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员宗世石报道）高玉香是河北省唐山市古冶区人，是子宫癌症患者，因家庭矛盾她的丈夫被两位哥哥砍伤致残，当地警方收受贿赂枉法裁判，高玉香因此到北京上访。近十年的上访诉求没有得到解决，多年的颠沛流离和多次的非法关押使她不幸患上了子宫癌，为了能在有生之年给丈夫讨回公道，她拖着病重的身体坚持在北京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>由于她长期在北京控告，地方政府开始了对她的打压。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日，正走在北京街头的高玉香被当地截访警察用手机定位的方式找到，强行带回古冶后，唐山市劳教委以高玉清于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日到北京总理驻地非法上访为由将她劳教一年。因为是癌症患者，唐山劳教所怕担责任拒收，古冶区政府不惜靠拉关系、走后门最终把高玉香关进了唐山市劳教所，一年的非法关押加之得不到有效的医治，使高玉香本已得到控制的病情复发且加重。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日，正在家中休息的高玉香又被警察抓走，以她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日去中南海地区非法上访为由又对她行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为了维护自己的信访权和人权自由权，最近高玉香一多次往返唐山－石家庄，控告当地政府非法关押、拘留、劳教上访人员，但河北省各级法院告知她，上面有通知，上访人员因拘留、劳教而提起诉讼起一律不受理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AGN9xLdUlaM/UmNJBIYxBeI/AAAAAAAApsk/N3ovjwWzY3w/s1600/IMG_5327.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AGN9xLdUlaM/UmNJBIYxBeI/AAAAAAAApsk/N3ovjwWzY3w/s320/IMG_5327.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FXwcIrbTrhk/UmNJDML2hmI/AAAAAAAApss/dWtEOiSkmsU/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+008.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FXwcIrbTrhk/UmNJDML2hmI/AAAAAAAApss/dWtEOiSkmsU/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+008.jpg\" width=\"218\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ysbYZT6EGsA/UmNJE23bc2I/AAAAAAAAps0/KBN8CB7MahE/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+009.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ysbYZT6EGsA/UmNJE23bc2I/AAAAAAAAps0/KBN8CB7MahE/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+009.jpg\" width=\"184\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oHFPJI2uB04/UmNJHBM8TcI/AAAAAAAAps8/3HKD6sB75qQ/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+010.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oHFPJI2uB04/UmNJHBM8TcI/AAAAAAAAps8/3HKD6sB75qQ/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+010.jpg\" width=\"203\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Qu9jAqCtj8s/UmNJHbKqFTI/AAAAAAAAptA/V9MU56Z2AyU/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+011.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Qu9jAqCtj8s/UmNJHbKqFTI/AAAAAAAAptA/V9MU56Z2AyU/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+011.jpg\" width=\"190\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}